               <p>DAVID BARBER. On the 10th of August I was in <placeName id="t18280911-319-crimeloc1639">Little Earl-street Seven-dials</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18280911-319-crimeloc1639" type="placeName" value="Little Earl-street Seven-dials"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18280911-319-crimeloc1639" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280911-319-off1637 t18280911-319-crimeloc1639"></join>; I felt a twitch at my pocket, and missed my handkerchief; I looked round and saw the prisoner with it in his hand - I called to him to stop; he put it under his coat, and ran down a court; I pursued him, and saw him take the handkerchief; it was taken from him at the watch-house; this is it; it is mine.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280911-319-person1742">
